Feature: Admin Dashboard

  As an admin
  When I log in
  So I can manage users

Background: admin exists
  Given the following funding sources exist:
  | email           | password |   Role  |
  | admin@admin.com | 1234abcd |  Admin  |

Scenario: admin dashboard
  When I go to the admin log in page
  And I fill form for "admin_email" with "admin@admim.com"
  And I fill form for "admin_password" with "1234abcd"
  And I press "Log in"
  Then I should be on admin dashboard
  Then I should see a button with "Users"
